bungholio
0 00391D3C Z // Run Speed.
0 01894E98 3FA0ZZ // Walking Speed Modifier (Hold O While Moving)
0 01894E9C 93A3030C // Walking Speed Modifier (Hold O While Moving)
0 01894EA0 C383030C // Walking Speed Modifier (Hold O While Moving)
0 01894EA4 48391EE2 // Walking Speed Modifier (Hold O While Moving)
0 00391EDC 49894E9A // Walking Speed Modifier (Hold O While Moving)
0 003923EC 38600001 // Disables the teleportation effect that happens when you run down steps or other things with very quick speed. Default value is 60000000.
[Z]3F8CCCCD=Default 1.1;3FC00000=1.5;40000000=2;40400000=3;40800000=4;40A00000=5[/Z]
[Z]4348=Default 200;4396=300;43C8=400;4448=800;44C8=1600;4548=3200;45C8=6400[/Z]
/*
Memory location of your
walking speed
0 01A9030C 43480000

The address is directly
supplied in the ASM from
the 2 lines at 00391ED8
and 00391EDC.

0 00391ED8 3C6001A9 lis r3,0x01A90000
0 00391EDC C383030C lfs f28,0x030C(r3) = 0x01A9030C
*/
#





































